headline: Electric Grid Enhancements to Benefit 5,000 JCP&L Customers in Morris, Passaic and Sussex Counties
summary: Jersey Central Power & Light (JCP&L), a subsidiary of FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE: FE), has begun construction on a comprehensive project designed to help prevent or minimize the impact of power outages for more than 5,000 northern New Jersey customers.
